cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CR 

The paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques for person recognition in social media photos. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning models, which falls under the category of cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also discusses the use of feature extraction and analysis, which falls under the category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning algorithms, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper also discusses the security and privacy implications of person recognition, which falls under the category of cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
